description: Number of symmetrical planar partitions of n: planar partitions (A000219) that when regarded as 3-D objects have only a threefold axis of symmetry, i.e. C3 symmetry.
links: Wouter Meeussen, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..151
example: The plane partitions {{3, 2, 2}, {3, 1}, {1, 1}} and {{3, 2, 2}, {3, 2}, {1, 1}} have C3 symmetry.
author: _Wouter Meeussen_
